Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:58.22,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,We are still living today{NOTE:僕ら今日も生きている}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.22,0:01:01.45,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,We are still laughing today{NOTE:僕ら今日も笑ってる}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.45,0:01:05.95,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,We don't need anything more{NOTE:それだけでもう何もいらない}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.95,0:01:07.82,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,Just RIDE ON{NOTE:今すぐRIDEON}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.82,0:01:11.12,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,We're quick to want{NOTE:僕らすぐに求める}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.12,0:01:14.32,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,This feeling is only natural{NOTE:欲張りな生き物さ}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.32,0:01:20.35,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,We're born without anything after all{NOTE:何も持たずに生まれてきたのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:22.12,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,Happiness is{NOTE:幸せは}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.12,0:01:25.19,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,To be by your side, to be close to you{NOTE:そばにあって　近くにあって}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.19,0:01:28.59,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,Not to lose sight of what is really important{NOTE:大切なものほど見えなくなるけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:29.89,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,To be grateful{NOTE:感謝して}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.89,0:01:34.92,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,To the person who understands no matter what happens{NOTE:何が起きたって分かってくれる人へ}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.92,0:01:37.92,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,Everyone is afraid{NOTE:誰にだって　逃げたくなって}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.92,0:01:41.35,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,To lose sight of oneself{NOTE:自分を見失いそうになるけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.35,0:01:49.32,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,But you will surely find love in your heart{NOTE:愛は必ず君の心にあるよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.32,0:01:54.55,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,Come walk with us{NOTE:僕ら一緒に歩いていこうよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:02:00.15,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,We're under the same sky, we look at the same stars{NOTE:同じ空のした　同じ空を見上げながら}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:05.22,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,Let's keep this beautifully colored bond{NOTE:美しい色の絆　数えていよう}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:08.45,OP/ED English,,0,0,0,,Happiness is forever{NOTE:幸せはいつも}
