Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:04.58,Episode,,0,0,0,,{\pos(670,350)\fad(550,550)}\NEpisode 56\N"A Lukewarm Kinship"{NOTE:第５6話\\Nクールでホットな絆}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:03.53,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,So that's a Channeling Gem…?{NOTE:これが絆珠…}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:08.29,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,We can use this to contain other monsters' kinship genes, correct?{NOTE:これにモンスターの絆遺伝子とやらを入れればいいのですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:09.66,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,Yep.{NOTE:そんダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:13.96,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,So where can we meet such monsters?{NOTE:それでそのモンスターはどこに行けば会えるんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:18.05,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,You need to find them by yourselves.{NOTE:それは自分自身で見つけるしかないダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:20.76,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,Each kinship is different.{NOTE:絆は人それぞれ違う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:23.59,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,Looking for it is part of your studying.{NOTE:それを探すのも修業だべ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:25.64,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,But…{NOTE:でも…}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:27.85,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,We need to act fast for Avinia's sake.{NOTE:早くしないとアユリアが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:30.85,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,Okay.{NOTE:分かったダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:48.16,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,There's a rumor that a very strong monster is on the other side of this mountain range.{NOTE:向こうの方にとても強いモンスターが出るという噂があるダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:51.21,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,You'll find something there, for sure.{NOTE:きっとそこで何かつかめるだべ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:53.46,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,Go on and try it.{NOTE:行ってみるといいダ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:57.25,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Should we? With such ambiguous information…?{NOTE:しかしあまりにも曖昧な情報では…}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.96,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.{NOTE:ありがとうございます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:04.01,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Let's just head in that direction for time being.{NOTE:取りあえずそちらの方向に向かってみよう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:05.09,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Very well.{NOTE:分かりました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:12.39,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,What matters is the kinship.{NOTE:大事なのは絆だべ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:37.75,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,So far there's only a snow-covered road up ahead.{NOTE:この先もずっとただの雪道でした。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:40.38,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,I didn't see any people or villages around here.{NOTE:人も村もまったく見当たりません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:42.05,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,I see…{NOTE:そっか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:45.09,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Why don't we use Rathi?{NOTE:どうしてレイアさんで飛んでいかないのですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:49.01,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,We may miss some monsters from the sky.{NOTE:空からだと例のモンスターを見逃してしまうからだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:52.14,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,It might take more time, but I think it'll be more effective to go by foot.{NOTE:時間はかかるけど歩いた方が確実だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:53.89,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,I see.{NOTE:なるほど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:55.98,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,By the way, Cheval.{NOTE:ところでシュヴァルさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:05:00.73,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,We share a pretty good relationship, don't you think?{NOTE:僕たちなかなかいい関係だと思いませんか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:05.61,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,For example, our fight with that Ebon Rider back then.{NOTE:この間のブラックライダーズとの戦い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:11.37,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,We didn't win, but I think it was pretty good team work regardless.{NOTE:勝てはしませんでしたが僕たちなかなかいいチームワークだったと思うのです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:12.29,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Yeah.{NOTE:ああ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:13.79,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,I think so too.{NOTE:確かに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:17.12,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Things went unexpectedly well for our first fight.{NOTE:初めてのわりにはうまくやれたかもね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:19.79,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,I'm glad you agree!{NOTE:やはりシュヴァルさんもそう思いますか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:23.55,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,If we awaken new powers within Rathi…{NOTE:あとはレイアさんさえ新しい力に目覚めれば…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:27.84,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,…I think in our next run-in with that Ebon Rider,\Nwe'll fight with much more composure.{NOTE:…次は必ずあのﾌﾞﾗｯｸﾗｲﾀﾞｰｽﾞに立ち向かえると思うのです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:29.30,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Yeah.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:31.72,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,It's also to protect everyone.{NOTE:みんなを守るためにもね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:34.14,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,But we can't let our guard down.{NOTE:でも油断は禁物だよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:37.73,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Cheval, you're quite careful.{NOTE:シュヴァルさんはなかなか慎重なのですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:39.77,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Which is exactly why it'll be okay.{NOTE:ですが大丈夫です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:41.94,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Just like our kinship.{NOTE:われわれの絆はそう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:45.32,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,It's an unbreakable kinship, just like the one between Lute and Navirou.{NOTE:リュートさんとナビルーのように固く結ばれているのです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:48.07,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Like Lute's…?{NOTE:リュートたちのように…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:50.41,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,That's right.{NOTE:そうです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:56.66,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,With our cool and hot kinship, we'll surely be able to save Avinia.{NOTE:われわれのクールでホットな絆があればきっとアユリアさんを助けることができるでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:58.88,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Cryo.{NOTE:頼りにしてるよ、クーリオ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:00.04,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:01.46,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Just leave it to me.{NOTE:お任せください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:11.47,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Cryo.{NOTE:クーリオ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:13.47,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Do you happen to have any Hot Drink with you?{NOTE:ホットドリンクは持ってる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:18.94,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,I am strong against the cold, so I didn't bring any.{NOTE:僕は寒さに強いのでﾎｯﾄﾄﾞﾘﾝｸは持っていないのです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:20.52,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.{NOTE:すみません…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:21.86,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,I see.{NOTE:そっか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:23.65,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,It's okay.{NOTE:そうだよね…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:27.78,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,I can handle it for now.{NOTE:これくらいの寒さなら何とかなるさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:30.91,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,I've already made a blunder… I'm sorry.{NOTE:早速の失態無念です…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:34.62,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,For time being, I will go check the situation ahead.{NOTE:取りあえず僕が先行して様子を確認してきます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:50.43,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,I'll go with you…{NOTE:俺も行くよ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:21.58,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.{NOTE:ごめんね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:22.83,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,I'll definitely come for you later.{NOTE:後で絶対…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:41.23,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Oh, I found a fugitive.{NOTE:脱走者み～っけ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:43.35,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,No, no, no.{NOTE:無理無理無理。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:46.23,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,It won't work without a proper key.{NOTE:そんなもんじゃそこの鍵は開かないって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:48.57,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,Please give me that key!{NOTE:その鍵を渡してください！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:50.90,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Hey, don't be so impatient.{NOTE:まあそう焦るなって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:58.04,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Hold on for now.{NOTE:今はこらえろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:00.16,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,You'll understand their goal soon enough.{NOTE:いずれやつの目的が分かる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:01.87,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,What…?{NOTE:あなた…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:03.71,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,What do you mean…?{NOTE:何を言っているのです？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:05.00,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Who knows?{NOTE:さあ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:08.34,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,If you value your Monstie,\Nyou'll return to your cell without making a fuss.{NOTE:あのオトモンが大事なら素直にろうに戻るんだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:30.15,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,It's getting hard to see…{NOTE:これは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:34.32,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Let me lead you.{NOTE:僕が先導しましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:37.20,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,It's time for my cold resistance to prove useful.{NOTE:ここは寒さに強い僕の出番です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:50.67,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Watch your step, Cryo!{NOTE:クーリオ気を付けて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:54.01,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,This is a snowstorm.\NThere's no telling what will happen.{NOTE:この吹雪だ。何が起きるか分からない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:55.63,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.{NOTE:大丈夫です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:57.18,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Please leave everything to me.{NOTE:僕に任せてください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:04.94,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Are you okay?{NOTE:大丈夫ですか!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:08.27,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Don't move!{NOTE:危ない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:17.45,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Cheval…?{NOTE:シュヴァルさん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:40.05,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Cheval.{NOTE:すみませんシュヴァルさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.51,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,You saved me!{NOTE:助かりました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:46.98,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Cheval?{NOTE:シュヴァルさん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:51.86,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?{NOTE:ケガはない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:54.07,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,I'm fine, but…{NOTE:僕は大丈夫ですが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:57.28,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,All right.{NOTE:よし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:58.66,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Then let's go.{NOTE:じゃあ行こう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:15.92,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Cheval!{NOTE:シュヴァルさん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:18.51,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Are you okay!?{NOTE:大丈夫ですか!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:21.43,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,I'm fine.{NOTE:大丈夫…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:27.23,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,I was thinking that you've been acting strange for a while…{NOTE:さっきからおかしいと思っていましたが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:28.64,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,You have terrible fever!{NOTE:ひどい熱です！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:31.36,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,It's not a problem.{NOTE:問題ないよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:32.36,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Let's go.{NOTE:行こう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:41.66,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,You're being too reckless!{NOTE:やっぱり無理です！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:43.99,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,We need to rest somewhere.{NOTE:一度どこかで休まないと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.17,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,I…{NOTE:僕が…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:58.47,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,I need to do something…{NOTE:何とかしないと…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:32.08,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Rathi!{NOTE:レイアさん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:33.63,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!{NOTE:ありがとうございます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:39.34,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,But…{NOTE:でも…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:41.43,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,This snowstorm just won't stop…{NOTE:この吹雪をずっとは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:57.52,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,"Please leave it to me", my paw!{NOTE:何が｢任せてください｣ですか…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:00.99,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,I'm…{NOTE:僕は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:02.86,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,I'm completely useless!{NOTE:まったく役に立てていない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:15.04,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,I'm going to search for something useful to Cheval!{NOTE:何かシュヴァルさんのために役立つものを探してきます！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:17.00,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,In the meantime, please take care of him!{NOTE:それまでの間お願いします！}
Comment: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:22.05,Default,Chapter,0,0,0,,Eyecatch
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:23.76,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:26.05,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Rathian!{NOTE:リオレイア！}
Comment: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:26.05,Default,Chapter,0,0,0,,#Black screen
Comment: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:28.06,Default,Chapter,0,0,0,,$Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:32.06,Default,Chapter,0,0,0,,Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:42.36,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,What was that?{NOTE:いったい何が…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:45.70,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,What is this place?{NOTE:ここは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:49.37,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Don't tell me…{NOTE:もしかしたら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:57.25,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,It was a village…?{NOTE:村…だったのでしょうか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:02.97,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,What on earth has happened in here?{NOTE:いったい何が…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:05.76,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,That's…!{NOTE:これは…！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:07.68,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,An alchemist shop signboard!{NOTE:調合屋の！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:12.14,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,An alchemist shop should have materials for restorative medicines.{NOTE:調合屋なら回復薬の材料が置いてあってもおかしくありません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:14.94,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,I can save Cheval with those.{NOTE:それがあればシュヴァルさんを助けられる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:26.24,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,A Barioth!?{NOTE:ベリオロス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:27.74,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,What's it doing here!?{NOTE:どうしてこんな所に!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:42.38,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,This is bad!{NOTE:まずい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:02.23,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Rathi…?{NOTE:レイア…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:03.98,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,You protected me…?{NOTE:お前が守ってくれたのかい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:07.24,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Where's Cryo?{NOTE:クーリオは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:08.99,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Rathi…{NOTE:レイア…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:11.53,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Can you find Cryo?{NOTE:クーリオを捜せるかい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:15.79,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:19.17,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Rathian!{NOTE:リオレイア！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:08.76,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,It won't attack…?{NOTE:襲ってこない…？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:18.39,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Cheval!{NOTE:シュヴァルさん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:19.89,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Rathi.{NOTE:レイア。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:20.77,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Let's go.{NOTE:いくよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:39.62,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Why…?{NOTE:どうして…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.21,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Why does it have so many scars?{NOTE:あんなに傷が？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:49.13,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Why won't it fly?{NOTE:なぜ飛ばないんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:52.38,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Rathi!{NOTE:レイア！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:55.47,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Hold on, Rathi!{NOTE:待って、レイア！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:16.91,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,I won't let you!{NOTE:させません！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:23.92,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,I won't let you lay a claw on Cheval!{NOTE:シュヴァルさんには指一本触れさせません！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:32.93,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Wait, both of you.{NOTE:待って二人とも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:38.47,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Cheval?{NOTE:シュヴァルさん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:44.69,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,I won't harm you or this village anymore.{NOTE:これ以上お前にもこの村にも危害を加えない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:47.65,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,So please, let's just end this battle.{NOTE:だから攻撃をやめてくれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:49.61,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,I don't want to fight with you.{NOTE:お前と争いたくないんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:58.33,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Please believe me.{NOTE:信じてくれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:00.70,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,We just want to save our friend.{NOTE:俺たちはただ友達を…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:04.33,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,We want to save Avinia.{NOTE:アユリアを助けたいだけなんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:10.75,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Do you know her…?{NOTE:アユリアを知っているのかい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:25.81,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,What's that?{NOTE:何です？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:28.86,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Could it be… the binding genes?{NOTE:もしかして…絆遺伝子？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:29.69,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Perhaps…{NOTE:これが!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:38.53,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,The Barioth went away…{NOTE:ベリオロスが去っていく…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:43.83,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Cheval!{NOTE:シュヴァルさん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:58.34,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,It's a recovery medicine I obtained.{NOTE:僕が調合した回復薬です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:00.39,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,You should feel a little better you if you drink it.{NOTE:飲めば少しは楽になるはずです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:06.85,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,How is it?{NOTE:どうですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:12.44,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,I feel much better.{NOTE:だいぶ楽になったよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:14.36,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,I'm glad to hear that.{NOTE:それはよかったです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:17.49,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Rathi is exhausted as well.{NOTE:レイアさんもすっかり疲れてしまっているので…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:21.28,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,So, let's spend the night here and head back tomorrow.{NOTE:…もう一晩ここで体を休めてから戻りましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:22.12,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Good idea.{NOTE:分かった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:28.04,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Cryo!?{NOTE:クーリオ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:34.42,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Thank you, Cryo.{NOTE:ありがとう、クーリオ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:41.89,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Thanks to you I'm feeling much better.{NOTE:クーリオのおかげですっかり良くなったよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:44.18,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,I'm glad.{NOTE:それはよかったです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:46.02,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,What about you, Cryo?{NOTE:クーリオは大丈夫？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:48.06,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,I feel good as new.{NOTE:まったく問題ありません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:52.40,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,But really…{NOTE:それにしても…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:54.90,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,What has happened to this village?{NOTE:いったいこの村はどうしたんだろう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:58.74,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,There's no one here, so I guess it wasn't the snowstorm.{NOTE:人はいないですし吹雪ではないでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:18:59.70,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Yes…{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:03.16,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,It's almost like it was destroyed by a monster…{NOTE:まるでモンスターに襲われたような…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:05.62,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Surely you don't think that the Barioth did it!?{NOTE:まさかあのベリオロスが!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:07.62,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.{NOTE:いや違うね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:10.29,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,He's guardian of this village.{NOTE:彼はこの村の守り神だよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:11.33,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Guardian?{NOTE:守り神？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:12.88,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Yes.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:16.59,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,He had a lot of old scars, so he must have fought a lot.{NOTE:あれだけの古傷を負い戦っている間も…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:18.51,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,He also didn't move at all.{NOTE:…じっとこの場で動かなかったのは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:23.51,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,I guess he must have kept on protecting this village, even now.{NOTE:…今まで村を守り続けていたからじゃないかな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:25.51,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,That means, he…{NOTE:すると彼は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:28.85,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,…protected this village all alone,\Neven though there's nobody here anymore?{NOTE:もう誰もいないこの村を今もたった一人で…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:31.77,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Hey!{NOTE:おーい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:35.32,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Hey!{NOTE:おーい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:38.57,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Lute?{NOTE:リュート。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:40.11,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?{NOTE:どうしてここへ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:42.07,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Dede Geezer said you stopped by.{NOTE:デデ爺に聞いたんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:45.37,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,And there was a snowstorm, so we got worried about you.{NOTE:嵐があったっていうから心配して来てみたんだけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:47.41,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,But looks like you're doing fine.{NOTE:…大丈夫だったみたいだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:49.16,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,It's thanks to Cryo.{NOTE:クーリオのおかげですよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:50.41,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,No, no.{NOTE:いえいえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:52.71,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to Cheval.{NOTE:シュヴァルさんのおかげですよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:54.42,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,By the way…{NOTE:ところで…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:56.63,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,What is this place?{NOTE:ここは何なのだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:19:58.21,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,We're not sure.{NOTE:分かりません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:20:01.09,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,We only know it was probably a village.{NOTE:たぶん村だとは思うのですが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:03.84,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Cheval, did you come here to train too?{NOTE:シュヴァルもここで修業してたのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:05.68,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Do you use snowmans?{NOTE:雪だるまか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:08.31,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Lute can handle up to two snowballs.{NOTE:リュートは２段積みまではクリアしたぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:12.44,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,What kind of training are you putting yourself through?{NOTE:いったいどんな修業をしてたのさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:14.94,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Ah, the head…!{NOTE:ああ！頭が！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:16.82,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Lute, you brute!{NOTE:リュートのXXだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:16.31,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Hm?{NOTE:おや？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:19.15,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,There's something here.{NOTE:ここに何かありますよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:29.04,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,What is it, I wonder?{NOTE:何でしょうか？これ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:31.08,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,What's written on it?{NOTE:何て書いてあるんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:38.00,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Did you finally get so dumb that you can't even read, Lute?{NOTE:リュートとうとう文字も読めないくらいおバカになってしまったのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:42.01,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,I can't read it because it's all scratched. Stupid Navirou.{NOTE:文字がかすれていて読めないんだよ。おバカナビルー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:45.18,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,What!? That's rude!{NOTE:な～!?おバカとは失礼だぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:46.68,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Stupid Lute!{NOTE:おバカリュート！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:49.35,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Stupid, stupid Navirou.{NOTE:おバカおバカナビルー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:51.39,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Stupid, stupid, stupid Lute!{NOTE:おバカおバカおバカリュート！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:53.94,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Stupid, stupid, stupid, stupid Navirou.{NOTE:おバカおバカおバカおバカナビルー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:56.56,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Stupid, stupid, stupid, stupid, stupid Lute!{NOTE:おバカおバカおバカおバカおバカリュート！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:59.32,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Stupid, stupid, stupid,\Nstupid, stupid, stupid…{NOTE:おバカおバカおバカおバカおバカおバカ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:01.90,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,…stupid, stupid, stupid, stupid Navirou!{NOTE:…おバカおバカおバカおバカナビルー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:02.90,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Heh.{NOTE:ヘッ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.87,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Do you have anything to say?{NOTE:何か言いたいことあるか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:07.91,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Yes, "poof"!{NOTE:うりー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:13.75,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Knock it off!{NOTE:やめろ～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:15.46,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Ah, it stinks!{NOTE:おわっ臭っ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:17.38,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,What are they doing…?{NOTE:何をしてるんですか…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:20.00,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,"In ancient times…"{NOTE:｢いにしえに…」}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:21.71,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,"…handing down…"{NOTE:「…伝わりし…」}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:23.17,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,"…the secret art…"{NOTE:「…秘術…｣}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:24.93,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,"…the flying ones…"{NOTE:｢…乗り人の…」}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:26.34,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,"…crystal…"{NOTE:「…結晶…｣}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:27.68,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,"…song…"{NOTE:｢…歌…」}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:29.18,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,"…cannot became one."{NOTE:「…一つとならん。｣}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:33.06,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,"The flying ones' crystal…"{NOTE:乗り人の結晶…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.06,0:21:35.02,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's referring to Kinship Stones?{NOTE:絆石のことでしょうか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:37.44,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Maybe this was a Riders' village?{NOTE:ここはライダー村だったのかな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:40.11,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Cheval.{NOTE:シュヴァルさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.11,0:21:41.19,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Yes.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:45.07,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,It's an inscription dedicated for the Barioth guardian.{NOTE:守り神のベリオロスに絆石と書かれた石版。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:48.78,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Furthermore, something destroyed this village.{NOTE:さらに何かに破壊されたこの村。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:51.58,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Looks like it's related to Avinia, doesn't it?{NOTE:アユリアさんと関係がありそうですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:54.45,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?{NOTE:いったい何の話をしてるんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.45,0:21:58.12,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Lute wants you to lower the conversation level so he can understand you.{NOTE:会話のレベルをリュートが分かるように下げてほしいのだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.12,0:22:02.05,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,I understand just fine.\NCan you lower it for Navirou, though?{NOTE:俺じゃなくてナビルーが分かるように下げるんだろ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.05,0:22:03.38,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,What's your problem?{NOTE:何だ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:06.34,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Wanna take a sniff of Navirou's fart again?{NOTE:またナビルーのおならを嗅ぎたいのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:11.39,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Did you two meet a Barioth, Cheval?{NOTE:シュヴァルたちはベリオロスに会ったのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:12.35,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Yeah.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.43,0:22:14.68,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way…{NOTE:そういえば…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.73,0:22:20.44,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,You put kinship genes into your Channeling Gem!{NOTE:絆遺伝子が入った絆珠だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.44,0:22:22.40,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,You can go through the Rite now!{NOTE:伝承ができるではないか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.99,0:22:28.49,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,O' slumbering kinship…{NOTE:眠れる絆の力よ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:30.78,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,…awaken!{NOTE:ここに目覚めよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.05,0:22:47.34,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Rathi has blue tint now!{NOTE:レイアさんが青くなった！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:22:48.47,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Cheval…{NOTE:シュヴァル…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.47,0:22:50.72,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,…Rathi got a power up!{NOTE:…レイアに新しい力が。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.72,0:22:51.60,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Yep.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:22:53.85,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Rathi!{NOTE:レイア！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.85,0:22:55.22,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Ice Cyclone!{NOTE:アイスサイクロン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.48,0:23:04.36,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Whoa!{NOTE:おお～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.36,0:23:07.03,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,That's a Barioth's Ice Cyclone!{NOTE:これはベリオロスのアイスサイクロン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.15,0:23:09.74,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,You did it, Cheval.{NOTE:やったなシュヴァル。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.74,0:23:10.66,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Yep.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:11.87,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Then…{NOTE:それじゃあ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.87,0:23:14.16,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,…let's go save Avinia!{NOTE:アユリアを助けに行こう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:15.49,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Cheval.{NOTE:シュヴァルさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.49,0:23:17.25,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,I will assist you the best I can.{NOTE:しっかりサポートしますよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.71,0:23:19.41,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Yeah.{NOTE:ああ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.17,0:23:21.88,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Cryo.{NOTE:頼むよクーリオ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.88,0:23:22.67,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Roger that!{NOTE:はい。}
