Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:30.88,Default,Papan,80,80,80,,I'm Papan.{NOTE:僕パパン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:32.64,Default,Papan,80,80,80,,The Royal Paleontology Scriveners' vice captain!{NOTE:書士隊の副隊長っす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.64,0:23:35.31,Default,Papan,80,80,80,,I'll finally be getting some screen time and…!{NOTE:僕にもとうとう活躍の場がきたっす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.31,0:23:38.02,Default,Papan,80,80,80,,…what!? I'm going to a dangerous place with Lilia!?{NOTE:…って！危険な所へリリアと調査!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:40.77,Default,Papan,80,80,80,,Captain Simone…!{NOTE:シモーヌ隊長～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.77,0:23:44.06,Default,Papan,80,80,80,,Next time:\N"It's Hard Being a Vice Captain!" Ride On!{NOTE:次回｢副隊長はつらいよ｣にライドオン！}
